</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C32ADAB5FFF50F51FF27F964CDEDF887" pageId="7" pageNumber="190" type="activity">
<paragraph id="8B8F893EFFF50F51FF27F964CDEDF887" blockId="7.[183,1390,1361,2223]" pageId="7" pageNumber="190">
<emphasis id="B944552CFFF50F51FF27F964CDD0F95F" bold="true" box="[183,421,1755,1788]" pageId="7" pageNumber="190">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Petter’s Big-footed Mouse is nocturnal and presumed to be exclusively terrestrial.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C32ADAB5FFF50F51FF29F891C811F8E8" box="[185,1124,1838,1867]" pageId="7" pageNumber="190" type="biology_ecology">
